metadata.name: Stallion of Mars #1
metadata.description: When mars rovers are searching for life in martian soil a mystical  creature is roaming the planet freely, and it has same characteristics of a wild horse, a stallion,  back on earth scientists are baffled to see a living creature on the red planet that has the traits like of horse on earth and humans are wondering if they can be domesticated when humans start to settle on the red planet, collect the unique portray of wild stallion in the art illustrated, the collection is of about 3K unique NFts on IPFS for you to have the exclusive piece for yourself for ever.
